                Flight School Must be FAA Certified
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="pb-2">
            <div class="flex flex-row">
              <div class="text-ideal-blue pr-3 font-extrabold">✓</div>
                More Experienced Instructors
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="pb-2">
            <div class="flex flex-row">
              <div class="text-ideal-blue pr-3 font-extrabold">✓</div>
                Geared Towards Career Pilots
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <p class="w-4/5 lg:w-3/5 grid place-items-center pb-20 text-lg text-center font-semibold">Ideal Aviation is one of the very few flight schools in the St. Louis area that is part 141.  We've even partnered with SWIC to provide flight training for college credit.</p>
